em)%20developer%20in%20the%20world%20based%20on%20its%20operational%2C%20under-construction%2C%20and%20awarded%20(PPA-contracted)%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Green%20Energy%20ranked%20second%20with%2018.1%20GW%2C%20followed%20by%20Canada-based%20Brookfield%20Renewable%20Partners%20with%2018%20GW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Flju3c01_adani-green-mercom_625x300_09_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ranking%20table%20shows%20the%20top%2010%20global%20large-scale%20(utility-scale)%20solar%20PV%20developers%20based%20on%20projects%20in%20operation%2C%20under%20construction%2C%20and%20awarded%20(PPA-contracted)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20note%20of%20the%20ranking%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20Adani%20Group%20chairman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20happy%20to%20see%20Mercom%20Capital's%20recent%20rankings%2C%20placing%20us%20second%20globally%20among%20the%20world's%20large-scale%20solar%20PV%20developers.%20This%20recognition%20underscores%20our%20continued%20and%20unwavering%20commitment%20as%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20renewable%20energy%20players%20in%20the%20world%20and%20on%20target%20to%20achieving%20our%20ambitious%20goal%20of%2045%20GW%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20by%202030.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20are%20happy%20to%20see%20Mercom%20Capital's%20recent%20rankings%2C%20placing%20us%20second%20globally%20among%20the%20world's%20large-scale%20solar%20PV%20developers.%20This%20recognition%20underscores%20our%20continued%20and%20unwavering%20commitment%20as%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20renewable%20energy%20players%20in%20the%20world%20and%20on...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Gautam%20Adani%20(%40gautam_adani)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgautam_adani%2Fstatus%2F1733317691115745778%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20top%20global%20solar%20developers%2C%20six%20were%20based%20in%20Europe%2C%20three%20in%20North%20America%2C%20and%20one%20was%20headquartered%20in%20South%20Asia.%20Project%20portfolios%20of%20the%20top%20developers%20were%20primarily%20located%20in%20North%20America%2C%20followed%20by%20Asia%20Pacific%2C%20Mercom%20Capital%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETotalEnergies%20was%20also%20the%20top%20company%20for%20under-construction%20and%20awarded%20(PPA-contracted)%20capacities%2C%20with%2029.3%20GW%20of%20projects.%20Brookfield%20Renewable%20Partners%20was%20the%20second-largest%20player%2C%20with%2013.6%20GW%2C%20followed%20by%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20with%2011.1%20GW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20year's%20report%20includes%20several%20new%20companies%2C%20primarily%20led%20by%20European%20developers%2C%20but%20with%20project%20portfolios%20spread%20around%20the%20world.%20Several%20leaders%20on%20the%20list%20are%20actively%20transitioning%20towards%20solar%20and%20other%20renewable%20energy%20sources...%26quot%3B%20Mercom%20Capital%20Group%20CEO%20Raj%20Prabhu%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20back%20of%20long-term%20PPAs%20of%2025%20years%20with%20central%20and%20state%20government%20entities%2C%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Ltd%20(AGEL)%20has%20leveraged%20its%20capabilities%20and%20expanded%20its%20presence%20across%2012%20states.%20The%20company%20deploys%20the%20latest%20technologies%20in%20its%20projects.%20With%20a%20portfolio%20of%2054%20operational%20projects%20and%2012%20projects%20under%20construction%2C%20AGEL%20is%20driving%20India%20on%20its%20renewable%20energy%20journey%2C%20the%20company%20says%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702105860000%2C%22v