was%20extra%20bounce%20here%20compared%20to%20Indian%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pace%20is%20a%20bit%20more%2C%20so%20will%20practice%20against%20pace%20bowling.%26quot%3B%20India%20will%20play%20the%20first%20of%20their%20three%20T20Is%20against%20the%20Proteas%20here%20on%20Sunday%20and%20Rinku%20is%20expected%20to%20bat%20at%20the%20crucial%20No.%205%20or%20No.%206%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20had%20also%20asked%20him%20to%20just%20play%20his%20natural%20game%20and%20bat%20at%20No.5%20or%20No.6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20practice%20session%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20it%20a%20lot%20because%20of%20the%20fine%20weather.%20Getting%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20Rahul%20Dravid%20sir%2C%20so%20that%20was%20a%20good%20feeling.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20continue%20playing%20the%20way%20I%20do%20and%20continue%20believing%20in%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinku%20told%20BCCI.tv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(He%20told%20me)%20to%20keep%20playing%20at%20No.%205%20or%206.%20It%20is%20tough%20to%20play%20in%20that%20position%2C%20but%20keep%20pushing%20yourself%20and%20believe%20in%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hard-hitter%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20added%20that%20batting%20in%20the%20two%20crucial%20positions%20since%202013%20had%20given%20him%20the%20confidence%20to%20play%20a%20similar%20role%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20playing%20for%20UP%20since%202013%20at%20No.%205%20or%206.%20So%2C%20I%20have%20got%20used%20to%20that%20position.%20I%20keep%20backing%20myself%20to%20play%20in%20that%20position%20because%20it%20is%20very%20tough%20to%20play%20in%20that%20position%20if%204-5%20wickets%20are%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinku%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20you%20have%20to%20build%20a%20partnership.%20So%20I%20keep%20telling%20myself%2C%20the%20more%20I%20can%20keep%20myself%20calm%2C%20the%20better%20it%20is%20(for%20me)%2C%20and%20not%20to%20react%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rinku.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20enjoy%20time%20out%20with%20fellow%20players%20to%20do%20well%20in%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%204-5%20players%20remain%20in%20a%20group.%20Me%2C%20Ravi%20(Bishnoi)%2C%20Arshdeep%20(Singh)%2C%20Avesh%20(Khan)%2C%20Jitesh%20(Sharma).%20We%20enjoy%20each%20other's%20company%2C%20which%20is%20very%20important%20in%20cricket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20remain%20fit%20in%20order%20to%20do%20well%20in%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702103580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F2837gh4o_rinku-singh_625x300_09_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwhen-i-batted-rinku-singh-sums-up-difference-between-india-and-south-africa-pitches-4648578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rinku%20Singh%20said%20that%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20had%20also%20asked%20him%20to%20just%20play%20his%20natural%20game%20and%20bat%20at%20No.5%20or%20No.6.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwhen-i-batted-rinku-singh-sums-up-difference-between-india-and-south-africa-pitches-4648578%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwhen-i-batted-rinku-singh-sums-up-difference-between-india-and-south-africa-pitches-4648578%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwhen-i-batted-rinku-singh-sums-up-difference-between-india-and-south-africa-pitches-4648578%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Ranbir%20spoke%20about%20his%20parents'%20fights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702103400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105849134%2Cimgsize-28312.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-when-ranbir-kapoor-talked-about-witnessing-frequent-fights-between-his-parents-rishi-kapoor-and-neetu-kapoor-called-his-life-a-fire-zone%2Farticleshow%2F105849134.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105849134.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERanbir%20Kapoor%2C%20the%20talented%20Bollywood%20actor%2C%20opened%20up%20about%20witnessing%20his%20parents'%20arguments%20and%20conflicts%20during%20his%20childhood.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20The%20Big%20Picture%2C%20he%20discussed%20how%20the%20media%20turned%20these%20disputes%20into%20headlines%2C%20causing%20embarrassment%20at%20school.%20However%2C%20Ranbir%20emphasized%20that%20his%20parents%20eventually%20reconciled%20and%20prioritized%20love%20and%20companionship%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20positive%20change%20in%20their%20relationship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Activist%20Nikhil%20Dey%20Among%20US%20Government%E2%80%99s%20International%20Anti-Corruption%20Champions%20for%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FNikhil_Dey_youtube.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Indian%20social%20activist%20Nikhil%20Dey%20was%20among%2011%20persons%20that%20the%20US%20government%20recently%20recognised%20as%20International%20Anti-Corruption%20Champions%20for%202023%2C%20citing%20his%20decades-long%20work%20to%20build%20peasant%20and%20worker%20empowerment%20campaigns%20and%20exposing%20corruption%20in%20the%20delivery%20of%20government%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDey%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Mazdoor%20Kisan%20Shakti%20Sangathan%20(MKSS)%2C%20which%20has%20led%20transparency%20and%20anti-corruption%20movements%20in%20India.%20The%20organisation%20is%20primarily%20based%20in%20Rajasthan%20that%20has%20led%20workers%E2%80%99%20and%20peasants%E2%80%99%20struggles%20for%20minimum%20wages%20and%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20December%207%2C%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Frecognizing-the-2023-anti-corruption-champions%2F%3Fs%3D31%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20past%2035%20years%2C%20activist%20Nikhil%20Dey%20has%20championed%20policy%20reforms%20to%20empower%20workers%20in%20India.%20He%20and%20his%20counterparts%20have%20brought%20to%20light%20official%20corruption%2C%20such%20as%20the%20underpayment%20of%20workers%20on%20official%20projects%2C%20and%20built%20peasant%20and%20worker%20empowerment%20campaigns%20targeting%20corruption%20in%20the%20delivery%20of%20government%20services.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20secretary%20of%20state%20Antony%20Blinken%20praised%C2%A0Dey%20for%20%E2%80%9Cworking%20with%20and%20for%20those%20harmed%20by%20corruption%2C%20and%20those%20particularly%20who%20are%20harmed%20most%20by%20it%3A%20underserved%2C%20marginalised%20populations%E2%80%9D.%20Blinken%20said%20Dey%20has%20helped%20communities%20in%20Rajasthan%20demand%20access%20to%20essential%20services%20and%20rights%20such%20as%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20fair%20wages%20and%20better%20working%20conditions.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20organization%20pioneered%20the%20practice%20of%20public%20audits%2C%20in%20which%20local%20officials%20have%20to%20report%20to%20communities%20how%20and%20where%20they%20spend%20the%20resources%2C%20and%20citizens%20have%20a%20chance%20themselves%20to%20ask%20probing%20questions%20of%20these%20officials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20These%20public%20audits%20spread%20across%20India%20and%20more%20citizens%20started%20taking%20the%20lead%20in%20holding%20officials%20to%20account%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Cat%20its%20heart%2C%20is%20how%20democracy%20needs%20to%20work%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20award%2C%20set%20up%20in%202021%2C%20recognises%20the%20US%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csupport%20for%20anticorruption%20leaders%20who%20put%20their%20lives%20on%20the%20line%20to%20spur%20lasting%20change%E2%80%9D.%20Dey%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20receive%20the%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010%20other%20International%20Anti-Corruption%20Champions%20for%202023%20recognised%20by%20the%20US%20government%20on%20Thursday%20were%20Stanislau%20Ivashkevich%20of%20Belarus%2C%20Jean-Claude%20Mputu%20of%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo%2C%20Arturo%20Torres%20of%20Ecuador%2C%20Ali%20(Mukhammedali)%20Toktakunov%20of%20Kyrgyz%20Republic%2C%20Marc%20N.%20Kollie%20of%20Liberia%2C%20Veronica%20Mihailov-Moraru%20of%20Moldova%2C%20Vladimir%20Novovic%20of%20Montenegro%2C%20Annette%20Planells%20of%20Panama%2C%20Francisco%20Belo%20Simoes%20da%20Costa%20of%20Timor-Leste%2C%20and%20May%20De%20Silva%20of%20Seychelles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F09114902%2FDIPNOTE-RESIZING-2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F09114902%2FDIPNOTE-RESIZING-2.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F09114902%2FDIPNOTE-RESIZING-2-300x150.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F09114902%2FDIPNOTE-RESIZING-2-1024x512.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewir