ltiple%20credits%20in%20a%20short%20period%20to%20minimize%20the%20negative%20impact%20of%20hard%20inquiries.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20highlights%20the%20significance%20of%20keeping%20old%20credit%20accounts%20open%20to%20maintain%20a%20longer%20credit%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22RAJNI%20PANDEY%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Favoid-these-6-mistakes-to-maintain-good-credit-score%2Farticleshow%2F105856653.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%20290%20Crore%20And%20Still%20Counting%20Among%20India's%20Biggest%20Cash%20Recoveries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20is%20likely%20India's%20biggest%20cash%20recovery%20in%20income%20tax%20raids%2C%20at%20least%20Rs%20290%20crore%20in%20hard%20cash%20has%20been%20recovered%20so%20far%20during%20raids%20in%20three%20states%20since%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20sum%20will%20rise%20as%20more%20cash%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20counted%20and%20officials%20have%20got%20intelligence%20about%20more%20locations%20where%20cash%20has%20been%20hidden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tax%20department%20raided%20the%20offices%20of%20an%20Odisha-based%20distillery%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETax%20department%20sources%20said%20up%20to%20seven%20rooms%20across%20the%20three%20locations%20and%20nine%20lockers%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20checked.%20The%20cash%20was%20found%20stuffed%20inside%20cupboards%20and%20other%20furniture.%20They%20said%20they%20have%20got%20information%20about%20other%20places%20where%20more%20cash%20and%20jewellery%20may%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20raids%20are%20being%20conducted%20at%20Boudh%20Distillery%20and%20offices%20linked%20to%20it%3B%20Baldev%20Sahu%20Infra%2C%20a%20group%20company%20of%20Boudh%20Distillery%2C%20and%20a%20rice%20milled%20owned%20by%20the%20same%20distiller