comment%20on%20Wednesday%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20validity%20of%20Section%206A%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%201955.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20have%20no%20knowledge%20of%20Assam's%20history%20should%20not%20speak.%20Assam%20was%20never%20a%20part%20of%20Myanmar.%20There%20were%20clashes%20for%20a%20brief%20period.%20That%20was%20the%20only%20relation.%20Otherwise%2C%20I%20have%20not%20seen%20any%20data%20which%20stated%20that%20Assam%20was%20a%20part%20of%20Myanmar%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20of%20words%20between%20Mr%20Sarma%2C%20known%20as%20the%20BJP's%20strategist%20for%20the%20northeast%2C%20and%20Mr%20Sibal%2C%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20who%20left%20the%20Congress%20in%20May%202022%2C%20also%20comes%20amid%20the%20crisis%20in%20Manipur%20where%20the%20issue%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20from%20Myanmar%20is%20a%20huge%20factor%20in%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20leaders%20including%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20have%20said%20entry%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20main%20factors%20behind%20the%20unrest%20in%20the%20northeast%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20proceedings%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Mr%20Sibal%20had%20said%20no%20migration%20can%20ever%20be%20mapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20history%20of%20Assam%2C%20you%20will%20realise%20that%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20came%20when.%20Assam%20originally%20was%20a%20part%20of%20Myanmar.%20And%20it%20was%20way%20back%20in%201824%20after%20the%20British%20conquered%20a%20part%20of%20the%20territory%20that%20a%20treaty%20was%20entered%20into%20by%20which%20Assam%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20British%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sibal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20imagine%20the%20kind%20of%20movements%20of%20people%20that%20must%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20then%20British%20empire.%20And%20if%20you%20jump%20to%201905%2C%20you%20have%20the%20partition%20of%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sibal%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20lawyer%20of%20some%20members%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20Manipur%2C%20following%20the%20hill-majority%20Kukis'%20ethnic%20clashes%20with%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20mention%20of%20Myanmar%20in%20sensitive%20public%20discourse%20has%20turned%20extremely%20emotive%20after%20what%20happened%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20Kuki%20tribes%2C%20who%20share%20kinship%20ties%20with%20tribes%20in%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20Mizoram%2C%20want%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur.%20Neighbouring%20state%20Mizoram%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20backing%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20Kukis%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMizoram's%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20Lalduhoma%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20he%20will%20meet%20Mr%20Shah%20and%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20in%20Delhi%20soon%20to%20discuss%20the%20issues%20of%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20displaced%20Kuki%20tribes%20from%20Manipur%20who%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20campaigning%20on%20November%204%2C%20Lalduhoma%20told%20NDTV%20it%20is%20their%20%26quot%3Bdream%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20all%20Mizo%20people%20under%20a%20single%20administrative%20unit.%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20saying%20goes%2C%20blood%20is%20thicker%20than%20water.%20The%20people%20from%20Manipur%20as%20well%20as%20Myanmar%2C%20they%20are%20our%20kith%20and%20kin%2C%20our%20flesh%20and%20blood.%20They%20are%20our%20brothers%20and%20sisters.%20We%20can't%20betray%20them%20when%20they%20are%20in%20a%20difficult%20situation...%20And%20regarding%20Zo%20unification%20or%20Greater%20Mizoram%2C%20whatever%20you%20call%20it%2C%20we%20all%20are%20behind%20this.%20It%20is%20the%20dream%20of%20the%20Mizos%20that%20a%20day%20will%20come%20when%20all%20the%20Mizo%20people%20divided%20due%20to%20the%20British's%20policy%20of%20divide%20and%20rule%20will%20be%20under%20a%20single%20administrative%20unit.%20That%20day%20will%20come%20one%20day.%20This%20is%20our%20dream.%20We%20are%20looking%20forward.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20private%20property%20of%20the%20MNF%20alone.%20It%20is%20a%20dream%20of%20all%20the%20Mizos.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMizoram%20has%20taken%20in%20over%2035%2C000%20refugees%20from%20the%20junta-ruled%20Myanmar%2C%20where%20the%20military%20forces%20are%20fighting%20ethnic%20insurgent%20groups%20and%20pro-democracy%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702096620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F60j3v1lo_kapil-sibal-himanta_625x300_09_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-was-never-part-of-myanmar-chief-minister-himanta-biswa-sarma-hits-back-at-kapil-sibal-4648425%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20hit%20back%20at%20lawyer%20Kapil%20Sibal%20for%20saying%20Assam%20was%20part%20of%20Myanmar%20during%20a%20hearing%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-was-never-part-of-myanmar-chief-minister-himanta-biswa-sarma-hits-back-at-kapil-sibal-4648425%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-was-never-part-of-myanmar-chief-minister-himanta-biswa-sarma-hits-back-at-kapil-sibal-4648425%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-was-never-part-of-myanmar-chief-minister-himanta-biswa-sarma-hits-back-at-kapil-sibal-4648425%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Viral%20Photos%20of%20the%20Week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702096200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105836300%2Cimg