sman%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20is%20renowned%20for%20his%20outspoken%20nature%20and%20refusal%20to%20remain%20silent%20when%20provoked.%20Beyond%20his%20aggressive%20batting%20prowess%2C%20Gambhir%20is%20known%20for%20his%20stylish%20retorts%20to%20critics%2C%20never%20shying%20away%20from%20speaking%20his%20mind.%20Recently%2C%20in%20a%20podcast%2C%20Gambhir%20shed%20light%20on%20a%20verbal%20altercation%20involving%20himself%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20and%20LSG%20pacer%20Naveen%20Ul%20Haq%20during%20the%20IPL%202023%20match%20between%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%20(RCB)%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fno-one-can-come-and-gautam-gambhir-on-virat-kohlis-spat-with-naveen-ul-haq%2Farticleshow%2F105854126.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hermes%20Heir%20Plans%20To%20Pass%20On%20%2411%20Billion%20Fortune%20To%20His%20Gardener%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20grandson%20of%20Hermes%20founder%20Thierry%20Hermes%20is%20reportedly%20planning%20to%20adopt%20his%2051-year-old%20gardener%20and%20leave%20him%20a%20%2411%20billion%20fortune.%20Citing%20Swiss%20publication%20%3Cem%3ETribune%20de%20Geneve%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFortune%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%20that%2080-year-old%20Nicolas%20Puech%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20making%20his%20%26quot%3Bformer%20gardener%20and%20handyman%26quot%3B%20his%20legal%20child.%20Notably%2C%20Mr%20Puech%20is%20a%20fifth-generation%20heir%20of%20Thierry%20Hermes%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20luxury%20fashion%20house%20in%201837.%20He%20is%20unmarried%20and%20childless%20and%20owns%20around%205%25%20-%206%25%20of%20the%20company%2C%20worth%20between%209%20billion%20and%20100%20billion%20Swiss%20francs%20(between%20%2410.3%20billion%20and%20%2411.4%20billion).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2Feurope%2F2023%2F12%2F07%2Fhermes-heir-planning-adopt-51-year-old-former-gardener-share-11-billion-fortune%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFortune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2080-year-old%20is%20now%20in%20the%20process%20of%20passing%20on%20the%20wealth%20to%20his%20former%20gardener.%20He%20has%20reportedly%20hired%20a%20legal%20team%20to%20take%20him%20through%20the%20process.%20He%20is%20also%20in%20the%20process%20of%20rearranging%20the%20benefactors%20of%20his%20estate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unnamed%20gardener%2C%20who%20is%20married%20to%20a%20Spanish%20woman%20with%20two%20children%2C%20now%20stands%20to%20inherit%20a%20significant%20share%20of%20Mr%20Peuch's%20wealth.%20Italian%20outlet%20%3Cem%3ESky%20TG24%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%2080-year-old%20had%20already%20handed%20the%20man%20the%20keys%20to%20a%20property%20in%20Marrakesh%2C%20Morocco%2C%20and%20a%20villa%20in%20Montreux%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20worth%20a%20combined%20total%20of%20%245.9%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Fortune%2C%20the%20move%20comes%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20effort%20by%20Mr%20Puech%20to%20reshape%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20his%20substantial%20estate%2C%20estimated%20at%20around%205%25%20or%206%25%20ownership%20of%20the%20%24220%20billion-valued%20Hermes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fpeach-fuzz-named-colour-of-the-year-2024-heres-what-it-stands-for-4648376%5C%22%3E'Peach%20Fuzz'%20Named%20Colour%20Of%20The%20Year%202024.%20Here's%20What%20It%20Stands%20For%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Mr%20Peuch%20quit%20the%20company's%20supervisory%20board%20in%20acrimonious%20circumstances%20after%20fashion%20rival%20LVMH%20acquired%2023%25%20of%20Hermes%20as%20part%20of%20a%20hostile%20takeover%20bid%2C%20largely%20by%20stealth.%20While%20his%20other%20family%20members%20set%20up%20a%20holding%20company%20with%20their%20shares%20to%20block%20a%20takeover%20by%20LVMH%2C%20Mr%20Puech%20held%20on%20to%20his%20stake.%20This%20feud%20with%20the%20family%20members%20appears%20to%20have%20influenced%20Mr%20Puech's%20unconventional%20choice%20of%20heir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Puech%20also%20faces%20challenges%20in%20realising%20his%20plan.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ch.ch%2Fen%2F%5C%22%3Ech.ch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adult%20adoptions%2C%20particularly%20in%20Switzerland%20where%20he%20resides%2C%20are%20rare%20and%20subject%20to%20complex%20requirements.%20An%20adult%20can%20adopt%20another%20adult%20if%20they%20lived%20together%20for%20at%20least%20a%20year%20when%20the%20adoptee%20was%20still%20a%20minor.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702095000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2Fkk72f5a8_hermes_625x300_20_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhermes-heir-plans-to-adopt-51-year-old-gardener-to-pass-on-11-billion-fortune-to-him-report-4648414%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20billionaire%20grandson%20of%20Hermes%20founder%20Thierry%20Hermes%20is%20reportedly%20planning%20to%20adopt%20his%2051-year-old%20gardener%20and%20leave%20him%20a%20%2411%20billion%20fortune.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhermes-heir-plans-to-adopt-51-year-old-gardener-to-pass-on-11-billion-fortune-to-him-report-4648414%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhermes-heir-plans-to-adopt-51-year-old-gardener-to-pass-on-11-billion-fortune-to-him-report-4648414%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhermes-heir-plans-to-adopt-51-year-old-gardener-to-pass-on-11-billion-fortune-to-him-report-4648414%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Polarising%20North-South%20Divide%20Narrative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20north%20versus%20south%20controversy%20has%20deepened%20after%20the%20BJP's%20win%20in%20three%20north%20Indian%20states%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20Congress'%20win%20in%20Telangana%2C%20a%20south%20Indian%20state%2C%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20debate%20was%20further%20fuelled%20by%20DMK%20MP%20DNV%20Senthil%20Kumar's%20remark%20on%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%205.%20Mr%20Kumar's%20controversial%20remarks%20on%20the%20heartland%20states%20were%20expunged%20from%20parliament%20records%20but%20only%20after%20a%20huge%20uproar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20social%20media%2C%20the%20controversy%20started%20with%20provocative%20tweets%20from%20Congress%20leaders%20Praveen%20Chakravarty%20and%20Karti%20Chidambaram%20on%20counting%20day.%20Two%20posts%20-%20Mr%20Chakravarty's%20'The%20South-North%20boundary%20line%20getting%20thicker%20and%20clearer!'%20and%20Mr%20Chidambaram's%3A%20'the%20South'%20-%20received%20a%20severe%20backlash.%20There%20were%20also%20posts%20scorning%20north%20Indians%20for%20voting%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20then%20migrating%20to%20southern%20states%20for%20jobs.%20Then%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20criticised%20the%20opposition%20parties%20and%20their%20supporters%20in%20an%20emoji-filled%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20north%20vs%20south%20binary%20or%20the%20regional%20parties'%20confrontational%20politics%20against%20so-called%20'outsiders'%20has%20defined%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20cities%20and%20the%20states%20in%20India.%20It%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20south%20and%20north%20voted%20differently.%20In%201977%2C%20the%20entire%20north%20voted%20against%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20south%20voted%20for%20the%20Congress.%20Nobody%20said%20anything%20then.%20Conversely%2C%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20south%20had%20non-Congress%20governments%20while%20the%20north%20was%20with%20the%20Congress.%20Nobody%20said%20anything%20then%20too.%20So%20why%20now%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20north-south%20talk%20by%20the%20so-called%20liberals%20is%20absurd.%20They%20want%20us%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20north%20is%20Hindu%20conservative%2C%20illiterate%20and%20backward-thinking%2C%20whereas%20the%20south%20is%20progressive%20and%20secular.%20Basically%2C%20it%20is%20an%20anti-Modi%20political%20construct%2C%20bereft%20of%20any%20merit.%20It%20is%20simply%20rooted%20in%20hatred%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20a%20political%20analyst%20from%20the%20south%20who%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20too%2C%20DMK%20leaders%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20consistently%20made%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20people%20from%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%20In%20Karnataka%2C%20Congress%20minister%20Priyank%20Kharge%2C%20who%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20son%20of%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20made%20negative%20comments%20against%20people%20from%20Hindi-speaking%20states%20migrating%20to%20the%20state%20for%20job%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectorally%20speaking%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20party%20which%20is%20confined%20to%20two%20south%20Indian%20states%3A%20Karnataka%20and%20now%20Telangana.%20The%20same%20people%20of%20Karnataka%20were%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP%20till%20May%202023%2C%20after%20which%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power%20promising%20freebies.%20Despite%20losing%20the%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20retained%20its%20total%20vote%20share%20of%2036%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20same%20as%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20though%20the%20Congress%20won%20the%20assembly%20elections%20this%20time%2C%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20has%20grown%20significantly.%20The%20party%20doubled%20its%20vote%20share%20from%207%20per%20cent%20in%202018%20to%2014%20per%20cent%20and%20managed%20to%20win%20eight%20seats.%20In%20the%202018%20Telangana%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20managed%20just%20one%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20if%20the%20BJP%20doesn't%20stand%20a%20chance%20to%20win%20elections%20on%20its%20own%2C%20the%20same%20goes%20for%20the%20Congress%20party.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20bitter%20relations%20with%20its%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20DMK%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20LDF%20in%20Kerala.%20Insiders%20say%20that%20the%20DMK%20won't%20cede%20more%20seats%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%202024%20parliamentary%20elections%20after%20its%20recent%20defeat.%20The%20Congress%20was%20looking%20to%20bargain%20for%2015%20seats%20from%20the%20DMK%20this%20time.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20DMK-led%20alliance%20won%2038%20of%20the%2039%20seats%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20DMK%20won%20all%20the%2020%20seats%20it%20contested%20while%20the%20Congress%20won%20eight%20of%20the%20nine%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20LDF%20(Left%20Democratic%20Front)%20in%20Kerala%20has%20always%20fought%20elections%20against%20the%20Congress-led%20UDF%20(United%20Democratic%20Front).%20Kerala%20is%20the%20lone%20state%20where%20the%20CPI(M)%20has%20an%20opportunity%20to%20make%20its%20presence%20felt%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha.%20So%2C%20any%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20is%20ruled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20its%20electoral%20success%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Congress%20may%20hope%20for%20its%20revival%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20elections%20to%20the%20state%20assembly%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20be%20held%20together.%20As%20of%20today%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20decided%20to%20fight%20on%20its%20own%20to%20improve%20its%20vote%20share.%20Only%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20and%20Jana%20Sena%20Party%20(JSP)%20have%20announced%20a%20formal%20alliance%20for%20the%202024%20elections%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndoubtedly%2C%20southern%20States%20have%20scored%20better%20than%20north%20Indian%20states%20in%20the%20metrics%20of%20health%2C%20education%20and%20economic%20growth.%20The%20southern%20states%20are%20also%20peeved%20about%20the%20inequity%20in%20revenue%20sharing%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20states%20and%20how%20the%20more%20prosperous%20states%20are%20being%20short-changed%20in%20the%20revenue%20sharing%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20often%20seen%20that%20when%20a%20regional%20party%20is%20apprehensive%20about%20losing%20its%20voter-base%20to%20a%20strong%20national%20party%2C%20it%20weaves%20a%20narrative%20lamenting%20about%20a%20north-south%20divide.%20We've%20seen%20this%20strategy%20adopted%20by%20several%20regional%20parties%20when%20the%20Congress%20had%20a%20strong%20presence%20nationally.%20The%20DMK%2C%20JD(S)%2C%20AIADMK%20used%20this%20tactic.%20Even%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20built%20its%20base%20depicting%20South%20Indians%20(particularly%20Tamils)%20as%20the%20enemy%20of%20the%20Marathi%20'manoos'.%20The%20strong%20rebuttals%20to%20the%20so-called%20imposition%20of%20Hindi%20were%20another%20way%20of%20asserting%20regional%20identity.%20Playing%20to%20the%20gallery%20is%20inherent%20in%20building%20regional%20parties%20and%20giving%20melodramatic%20turns%20by%20using%20language%20as%20a%20tool%20gets%20quick%20attention.%20In%20their%20quest%20for%20survival%2C%20these%20parties%20play%20to%20their%20local%20audience%2C%20projecting%20the%20BJP%20as%20a%20north%20Indian%20party%20incapable%20of%20addressing%20specific%20concerns%20of%20the%20states.%20And%20that%20the%20state's%20language%2C%20culture%2C%20honour%20can%20be%20safeguarded%20only%20by%20the%20respective%20regional%20parties%20and%20therefore%2C%20more%20power%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20states%20in%20the%20federal%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polarising%20narrative%20rankles%2C%20for%20many.%20Chandrasekhar%20K%20from%20Kerala%20has%20worked%20in%20five%20states%20across%20India.%20Speaking%20from%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20north-south%20divide%20is%20for%20those%20who%20have%20not%20ventured%20out%20of%20their%20state.%20Anyone%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20states%20within%20our%20country%20knows%20that%20people%20find%20ways%20to%20communicate%20and%20live%20together.%20Divisions%20are%20created%20by%20political%20parties%20to%20outmanoeuvre%20one%20another%20in%20garnering%20voters'%20support.%20People%20are%20smart%20and%20politically%20savvy%20in%20our%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20less%20educated%20people%20engaging%20in%20discussions%20on%20politics%20in%20tea%20stalls%20in%20north%20India.%20Interest%20and%20awareness%20matters.%20Many%20educated%20people%20don't%20care%20about%20politics%20or%20even%20voting%2C%26quot%3B%20adds%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702094760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Fpsgcbhj4_voting-generic_625x300_12_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-polarising-north-south-divide-narrative-4648408%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20north%20versus%20south%20controversy%20has%20deepened%20after%20the%20BJP's%20win%20in%20three%20north%20Indian%20states%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20Congress'%20win%20in%20Telangana%2C%20a%20south%20Indian%20state%2C%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-polarising-north-south-divide-narrative-4648408%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-polarising-north-south-divide-narrative-4648408%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22