pecially%20in%20the%20upper%20frequencies%2C%20but%20the%20Q30's%20ear%20cups%20also%20offer%20solid%20passive%20noise%20isolation%20which%20helps%20to%20defray%20some%20of%20the%20ambient%20annoyances%20in%20your%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnker's%20Soundcore%20headphones%20consistently%20punch%20above%20their%20weight%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20sound%20performance%2C%20and%20the%20Q30%20hold%20their%20own%20in%20this%20department%2C%20especially%20after%20a%20few%20tweaks%20to%20the%20hefty%20bass%20in%20the%20Soundcore%20mobile%20app%20for%20Android%20or%20iOS.%20There%20you%20can%20also%20customize%20other%20settings%2C%20swap%20between%20three%20noise-cancelling%20modes%2C%20and%20engage%20the%20available%20sleep%20mode%20to%20activate%20ambient%20sounds%20as%20you%20drift%20off%20on%20your%20commute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Q30%20fit%20comfortably%20thanks%20to%20solid%20padding%20for%20extended%20listening%20sessions%20and%20collapse%20for%20travel.%20Convenience%20features%20like%20Multipoint%20Bluetooth%20pairing%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20activate%20transparency%20mode%20by%20holding%20your%20hand%20on%20the%20right%20ear%20cup%20recall%20fancier%20models%20that%20cost%20double%20or%20triple%20the%20price%2C%20while%20their%20massive%20battery%20life%20is%20among%20the%20best%20you'll%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20after%20a%20solid%20pair%20of%20noise%20cancelers%2C%20but%20simply%20can't%20stomach%20the%20high%20prices%20of%20other%20top%20models%2C%20Anker's%20Soundcore%20Q30%20are%20a%20very%20enticing%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20features%3A%20Sony%20WH-1000XM5%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223597%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20black%20Sony%20WH-1000XM5%20wireless%20noise-cancelling%20headphones.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F634655a1d2050f0011d3e717%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222698%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3