ng%20headphones%20for%20consideration%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20best%20noise-cancelling%20headphones%2C%20we%20them%20as%20we%20would%20in%20our%20daily%20lives%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20for%20how%20they'll%20perform%20for%20a%20typical%20listener.%20That%20includes%20evaluating%20features%20like%20ease%20of%20setup%20with%20different%20kinds%20of%20source%20devices%2C%20comfort%2C%20battery%20life%2C%20and%20general%20usability.%20We%20assess%20sound%20quality%20by%20listening%20to%20music%20across%20multiple%20genres%20from%20common%20streaming%20services%20as%20well%20as%20in%20high%20resolution.%20We%20also%20play%20videos%20for%20features%20like%20spatial%20audio%20and%20head%20tracking%20with%20stereo%20and%20Dolby%20Atmos%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20noise%20cancelling%20and%20transparency%20mode%2C%20we%20include%20real-world%20testing%20in%20natural%20environments%20and%2C%20whenever%20possible%2C%20situations%20like%20plane%20flights%20or%20train%20commutes.%20For%20these%20products%2C%20we%20also%20incorporated%20a%20sound-treated%20room%20and%20professional%20stereo%20monitors%20to%20reproduce%20sounds%20like%20airplane%20noise%2C%20voices%2C%20and%20other%20effects.%20Battery%20testing%20includes%20putting%20the%20headphones%20on%20a%20stopwatch%20at%20medium%20volume%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20live%20up%20to%20their%20claims%2C%20or%20come%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENoise-cancelling%20headphones%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sony%20WH-1000XM5%20wireless%20noise-cancelling%20headphones%20in%20black.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F627c1d06dd983300191ca328%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20noise%20cancelling%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENoise%20cancellation%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Active%20Noise%20Cancellation%20(ANC)%20or%20Adaptive%20Noise%20Cancellation%2C%20is%20a%20technology%20designed%20to%20suppress%20sounds%20in%20your%20immediate%20environment.%20Noise-cancelling%20headphones%20are%20outfitted%20with%20tiny%20microphones%20which%20bring%20in%20ambient%20sounds.%20They%20then%20use%20onboard%20circuitry%20to%20analyze%20the%20sound%20in%20real%20time%2C%20flipping%20the%20polarity%20of%20the%20frequencies%20(essentially%20reversing%20their%20waveforms)%20to%20%26quot%3Bcancel%26quot%3B%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoise%20cancellation%20is%20an%20imperfect%20science%20and%2C%20as%20of%20yet%2C%20it's%20not%20able%20to%20block%20out%20all%20of%20the%20sounds%20in%20a%20given%20environment.%20That%20said%2C%20with%20each%20iteration%2C%20the%20best%20noise-cancelling%20headphones%20and%20earbuds%20increase%20how%20much%20sound%20they%20can%20block%2C%20especially%20at%20higher%20frequencies%20which%20are%20generally%20the%20hardest%20to%20cancel.%20The%20better%20the%20noise%20cancellation%2C%20the%20more%20frequencies%20are%20blocked%2C%20and%20the%20more%20noises%20your%20headphones%20can%20reduce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20over-ear%20headphones%20better%20than%20earbuds%20for%20noise%20cancelling%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20gap%20between%20over-ear%20headphones%20and%20earbuds%20was%20once%20more%20prominent%2C%20today's%20top%20noise-cancelling%20earbuds%20are%20close%20to%20or%20on%20par%20with%20the%20best%20noise-cancelling%20headphones%20that%20use%20an%20over-ear%20design.%20Both%20types%20offer%20good%20passive%20noise%20isolation%2C%20and%20both%20also%20use%20a%20mix%20of%20advanced%20hardware%20and%20software%2C%20including%20multiple%20microphones.%20While%20it%20varies%20case%20by%20case%2C%20you%20can%20get%20very%20effective%20noise%20cancelling%20in%20either%20over-ear%20headphones%20or%20earbuds%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20transparency%20mode%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETransparency%20mode%2C%20also%20called%20ambient%20audio%20(or%20someti