0papers%20of%20Northcutt%20Ely%2C%20a%20storied%20water%20attorney%20who%20argued%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20case%20Arizona%20v.%20California%20on%20the%20latter's%20behalf%2C%20and%20Ray%20Lyman%20Wilbur%2C%20a%20former%20secretary%20of%20the%20interior%20who%20oversaw%20construction%20of%20the%20Hoover%20Dam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20he%20felt%20living%20in%20the%20archives%20while%20some%20of%20his%20college%20compatriots%20partied%2C%20Hamby%20quipped%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20you%20could%20only%20be%20in%20the%20archives%20in%20the%20daytime.%20There%20were%20other%20opportunities%20in%20the%20nighttime%2C%20which%20I%20did%20not%20exploit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoerink%2C%20the%20environmentalist%2C%20compared%20Hamby%20to%20the%20historical%20figures%20he%20studied%20who%20fought%20to%20protect%20the%20system%20that%20has%20guaranteed%20California's%20water.%20%26quot%3BNorthcutt%20Ely%20and%20J.B.%20are%20saying%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20same%20things%2C%20that%20development%20elsewhere%20ultimately%20impacts%20the%20rights%20of%20California%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%2F%3Ffbid%3D2366464430299136%26set%3Dpb.100008068055824.-2207520000%5C%22%3EFacebook%20post%20celebrating%20his%20graduation%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Stanford%2C%20Hamby%20included%20a%20picture%20of%20himself%20smiling%2C%20diploma%20in%20hand%2C%20alongside%20a%20quote%20from%20John%20Wesley%20Powell%2C%20the%20one-armed%20explorer%20who%20led%20the%20first%20U.S.-sponsored%20expedition%20down%20the%20Colorado%20River%20and%20tried%20to%20help%20shape%20early%20American%20policy%20along%20the%20waterway%2C%20arguing%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwest.stanford.edu%2Fworks%2Fflow-change-state-boundaries-and-water-management-las-vegas%5C%22%3Ethere%20wasn't%20enough%20water%20to%20support%20mass%20Western%20expansion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20now%20ready%20to%20start%20on%20our%20w