nya%20Roy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20freezing%20temperatures%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20this%20demolition%20affects%20the%20lives%20of%20more%20than%20200%20displaced%20families%20of%20Sunder%20Nagar.%20Their%20homes%20were%20bulldozed%2C%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Affairs%20(MOHUA)%2C%20and%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2F2023%2Fnov%2F24%2Fdelhi-high-court-declines-to-stay-drive-to-demolish-slum-cluster-2635764.html%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20stay%20the%20demolition%20drive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Just%20across%20the%20road%20from%20the%20iconic%20Sunder%20Nursery%2C%20flanked%20by%20the%20World%20Heritage%20Site%20Humayun%E2%80%99s%20Tomb%2C%20this%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%3C%2Fem%3E%20features%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Urban%20Shelter%20Improvement%20Board%E2%80%99s%20(DUSIB%E2%80%99s)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdelhishelterboard.in%2Fmain%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FJJBastisList675.pdf%5C%22%3Elist%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20675%20%E2%80%98protected%E2%80%99%20jhuggi-jhopdi%20clusters.%20While%20demolishing%20these%20settlements%2C%20authorities%20must%20comply%20with%20protocols%20drawn%20out%20in%20a%202015%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdelhishelterboard.in%2Fmain%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F01%2FProtocol-1.pdf%5C%22%3Epolicy%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Slum%20and%20JJ%20Rehabilitation%20%26amp%3B%20Relocation%20Policy%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Land%20and%20Development%20Office%20(L%26amp%3BDO)%20allegedly%20flouted%20several%20protocols%20while%20carrying%20out%20the%20demolition.%20The%202015%20policy%20mandates%20that%20alternate%20rehabilitation%20must%20be%20provided%2015%20days%20prior%20to%20demolition.%20Pyare%20Lal%20(52)%2C%20a%20resident%20who%20works%20as%20a%20scrap%20dealer%2C%20said%20that%20notices%20announcing%20the%20demolition%20were%20pasted%20only%20three%20days%20earlier%2C%20i.e.%20on%20November%2018.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20the%20notice%20sent%20us%20into%20panic%2C%20then%20we%20heard%20rumours%20that%20the%20demolition%20would%20be%20stayed.%20And%20then%20suddenly%20the%20bulldozers%20came.%20We%20had%20no%20time%20to%20find%20a%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08125316%2FSR-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08125316%2FSR-3.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08125316%2FSR-3-300x224.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688270%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EResidents%20and%20policemen%20look%20on%2C%20each%20with%20different%20emotions%2C%20as%20the%20bulldozers%20wreak%20havoc%20on%20the%20basti.%20Photo%3A%20Sukanya%20Roy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20residents%20added%20that%20they%20did%20not%20possess%20the%20financial%20means%20to%20rent%20accommodation%20at%20such%20short%20notice.%20A%20majority%20of%20them%20are%20daily-wage%20earners%2C%20domestic%20workers%20and%20scrap%20collectors.%20The%20DUSIB%20has%20failed%20to%20provide%20alternate%20rehabilitation%20to%20even%20a%20single%20displaced%20family.%20The%20policy%20also%20mentions%20that%20alternate%20rehabilitation%20must%20be%20provided%20within%20five%20kilometres%20from%20the%20site%20of%20a%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegularity%20of%20livelihood%20and%20education%20are%20crucial%20to%20the%20displaced%20families%20of%20Sunder%20Nagar.%20Nasira%20Bibi%20(33)%20works%20as%20a%20domestic%20worker%20in%20a%20posh%20bungalow%20nearby.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20move%20far%20aw