g%20through%20the%20rubble.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20poor%20boy%20did%20not%20get%20time%20to%20even%20change%20clothes%20or%20eat%20lunch.%20What%20consolation%20could%20I%20possibly%20offer%20him%3F%20His%20future%2C%20all%20our%20futures%20seem%20bleak%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20Chandni%20(14)%20echoed%20a%20similar%20sentiment.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20is%20saying%20that%20we%20will%20go%20back%20to%20our%20village%20after%20my%20final%20exam%E2%80%A6%20and%20you%20know%20what%20will%20happen%20there%E2%80%A6%20I%20will%20have%20to%20quit%20my%20studies%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20relatives%20will%20get%20me%20married%20off.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08130954%2FSR5.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08130954%2FSR5.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08130954%2FSR5-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688276%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22678%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20child%E2%80%99s%20cot%20lies%20empty%20in%20a%20house%20that%20was%20due%20to%20be%20demolished%20the%20next%20day.%20Photo%3A%20Sukanya%20Roy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08131147%2FSR-6.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08131147%2FSR-6.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2