is%20under%20way%20for%20a%20two-year-old%20boy%20who%20was%20snatched%20in%20a%20street%20in%20Australia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A444%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjax-wilson-urgent-search-for-toddler-who-was-snatched-in-street-in-australia-13025445%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjax-wilson-urgent-search-for-toddler-who-was-snatched-in-street-in-australia-13025445%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjax-wilson-urgent-search-for-toddler-who-was-snatched-in-street-in-australia-13025445%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Strife-Torn%20Manipur%20Lifts%20Alcohol%20Ban%2C%20Civil%20Society%20Opposes%20Move%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Manipur%20cabinet%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanipur-no-more-a-dry-state-as-cabinet-legalises-liquor%2Farticleshow%2F105773378.cms%5C%22%3Elifted%20a%20nearly%2030-year-old%20ban%20on%20liquor%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20as%20the%20state%20continues%20to%20be%20embroiled%20in%20ethnic%20conflict%20and%20violence%20that%20began%20six%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20been%20a%20dry%20state%20since%201991%20after%20it%20enacted%20the%20%E2%80%9CManipur%20Liquor%20Prohibition%20Act%E2%80%9D%20in%201991.%20However%2C%20in%202022%20it%20partially%20lifted%20prohibition%20to%20boost%20the%20economy%20and%20tackle%20the%20problem%20of%20illegally%20produced%20alcohol%20and%20associated%20health%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20cabinet%20on%20Monday%20(December%204)%20approved%20manufacture%2C%20production%2C%20possession%2C%20export%2C%20import%2C%20transport%2C%20purchase%2C%20sale%20and%20consumption%20of%20liquor.%20The%20meeting%20was%20headed%20by%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20cited%20in%20the%20report%2C%20the%20state%20government%20is%20expecting%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20around%20Rs%20600-700%20crore%20post%20liquor%20legalisation%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanipur-no-more-a-dry-state-as-cabinet-legalises-liquor%2Farticleshow%2F105773378.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Coalition%20Against%20Drugs%20and%20Alcohol%20(CADA)%20and%20All%20Manipur%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Social%20Reformation%20and%20Development%20Samaj%20(Nupi%20Samaj)%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20state%20cabinet%E2%80%99s%20resolution%20to%20legalise%20liquor%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENupi%20Samaj%20president%20Th%20Ramani%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstiff-opposition-to-liquor-legalisation-nupi-samaj-questions-timing%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20while%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20are%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20their%20near%20and%20dear%20ones%2C%20the%20state%20government%20is%20concerned%20about%20the%20production%20of%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20not%20taking%20any%20decision%20to%20resolve%20the%20crisis%20and%20giving%20attention%20to%20liquor%20while%20the%20state%20is%20facing%20such%20a%20difficult%20situation%20is%20extremely%20unfortunate%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstiff-opposition-to-liquor-legalisation-nupi-samaj-questions-timing%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20dry%20state%20since%201991%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%201991%20Act%20allowed%20exemptions%20to%20scheduled%20caste%20(SC)%20and%20scheduled%20tribe%20(ST)%20communities%20to%20produce%20liquor%20under%20their%20traditional%20system%20and%20customary%20laws%2C%20the%20state%20cabinet%20on%20September%2020%2C%202022%2C%20had%20partially%20lifted%20the%20prohibition%20for%20others%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lift%20allowed%20sale%20and%20consumption%20of%20liquor%20at%20the%20district%20headquarters%2C%20hotels%20having%20not%20less%20than%2020%20beds%2C%20and%20the%20locally%20brewed%20country%20liquor%20would%20be%20exported%20outside%20the%20state%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanipur-no-more-a-dry-state-as-cabinet-legalises-liquor%2Farticleshow%2F105773378.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Confederation%20of%20Indian%20Alcoholic%20Beverage%20Companies%20(CIABC)%2C%20the%20apex%20body%20of%20the%20Indian%20alcoholic%20beverages%20industry%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Falcohol-association-welcomes-manipur-s-move-to-lift-prohibition-on-liquor-123120600902_1.html%5C%22%3Ewelcomed%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20latest%20move%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702029658000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fstrife-torn-manipur-lifts-alcohol-ban-civil-society-opposes-move%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Civil%20society%20organisations%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20state%20cabinet%E2%80%99s%20resolution%20to%20legalise%20liquor%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fstrife-torn-manipur-lifts-alcohol-ban-civil-society-opposes-move%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NFL%20coach%20apologises%20for%20using%209%2F11%20hijackers%20as%20example%20of%20teamwork%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702026