onal%20Awards%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98Isaignani%E2%80%99%20(the%20musical%20sage)%20and%20was%20conferred%20the%20title%20%E2%80%98Maestro%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Royal%20Philharmonic%20Orchestra%2C%20London%2C%20being%20the%20first%20Asian%20composer%20to%20record%20a%20symphony%20with%20them%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20credited%20with%20changing%20the%20way%20music%20is%20made%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247945%2Fsp-balasubrahmanyam-spb-padma-vibhushan-award-2021-singer-music-world-record-roja-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Tamil%20films.%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20composers%20to%20use%20Western%20classical%20music%20and%20arrangements%20in%20his%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Tamil%20cinema%2C%20he%20has%20also%20scored%20music%20for%20Telugu%2C%20Kannada%2C%20Malayalam%20and%20Hindi%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3ECheeni%20Kum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EPaa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20humble%20background%20and%20upbringing%20heavily%20influenced%20his%20musical%20journey%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20his%20music%20infused%20with%20elements%20of%20regular%2C%20everyday%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20biopic%20on%20the%20maestro%20is%20in%20the%20making%20and%20actor%20Dhanush%20will%20reportedly%20essay%20the%20role.%20According%20to%20the%20reports%2C%20the%20film%20will%20go%20on%20floors%20in%202024%20and%20be%20released%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilm%20trade%20analyst%20Manobala%20Vijayabalan%20confirmed%20the%20news%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3