20Sanjay%20Leela%20Bhansali%E2%80%99s%20directorial%20debut%20was%20well%20ahead%20of%20its%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20become%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20voice%2C%20CODAs%20grow%20up%20a%20little%20too%20quickly%2C%20often%20shedding%20innocence%20and%20befriending%20maturity%20at%20a%20tender%20age.%20These%20children%20form%20the%20bridge%20between%20the%20Deaf%20and%20hearing%20worlds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20article%20aims%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20these%20young%20people%20doing%20incredible%20work%20for%20their%20loved%20ones%20and%20bring%20forward%20their%20lives%2C%20issues%2C%20and%20stories%20in%20everyday%20parlance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Ffacts-about-sign-language-1-1-1700576918.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Ffacts-about-sign-language-1-1-1700576918.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Ffacts-about-sign-language-1-1-1700576918-300x162.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Ffacts-about-sign-language-1-1-1700576918-500x269.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Ffacts-about-sign-language-1-1-1700576918-768x413.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Ffacts-about-sign-language-1-1-1700576918-150x81.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334627%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22646%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bid.org.uk%2Flatest-news%2Flatest-news%2Fpost%2F264-7-facts-about-sign-language%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFollow%20this%